OL,6,FThe Lancashire Constabulary member of
OL,7,Fstaff admitted; eight offences of
OL,8,Fmisconduct in a public office,
OL,9,Fincluding sharing images taken from a
OL,10,Fscene of sudden death; sharing body
OL,11,Fworn footage and images of injuries to
OL,12,Fa suspect; sharing images taken from
OL,13,Fthe scene of a suspicious death; and
OL,14,Fdisclosing sensitive information to a
